high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the black end table on the wall, across from the couch.
Pick up the keys that are behind the white vase, on the black end table.
Turn around and go through the living room, to the purple ottoman.
Place the keys on the left side of the cell phone, on the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Put the keys on the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward toward the wall, then turn right, step forward and then turn left to face the small table.
Pick up the keys on the table.
Turn around and go right, go around the coffee table and go straight to go to the chair with the ottoman.
Put the keys on the ottoman, to the left of the cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Move the keys to the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the end of the sofa, then turn right then left to face the table
Pick up the keys from the table
Turn around and go to the chair then turn right and go to the fireplace and go around the coffee table and head to the ottoman
Put the keys on the ottoman
anns.task_desc: Move the keys from the table to the ottoman
